					<description><![CDATA[Trump announces tariffs on eight European allies for taking part in a joint military exercise, after threatening to annex the island.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<aside class="right-rail__container right-rail__container--ad"><div class="right-rail__ad__wrapper right-rail__module"><div class="right-rail__ad" id="right-rail__ad-7347120"></div></div>
