<p>&#8220;Our position on Greenland is very clear&mdash;it is part of the Kingdom of Denmark and its future is a matter for the Greenlanders and the Danes,&#8221; he continued.</p>



<p>French President Emmanuel Macron called the tariffs &#8220;unacceptable.&#8221; </p>



<p>&#8220;No intimidation nor threat will influence us, neither in Ukraine, nor in Greenland, nor anywhere else in the world when we are confronted with such situations,&#8221; he said. </p>



