<p>&ldquo;We live in a world where destabilizing powers have awakened,&rdquo; Macron said.</p>



<p>&ldquo;We are seeing certainties that sometimes lasted for decades being called into question, and Europe is being shaken in some of its certainties,&rdquo; he said. Europe &ldquo;sometimes has allies that we thought were predictable, always by our side, who are now causing us to have serious doubts, or even turning on those who doubted the least.&rdquo;</p>



<p>The United Kingdom, Germany, Sweden and Norway have also sent troops to take part in the military exercise, Operation Arctic Endurance.  </p>



